&lt;h1&gt;The Opensource dilemma&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a first-time opensource contributor and find opensource overwhelming? Does it happen that everyone’s been talking only about good things, and you are struggling to find the time or motivation to contribute? In this article, &lt;a href=&quot;https://princiya.com/blog/reality-of-opensource-contributions/&quot;&gt;Princiya Sequiera&lt;/a&gt; shares tips on how to make the most of hacktoberfest.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
